import React from "react";
import { Container, List, Elements, Links,ContainerMobile,
    ListMobile,
    ElementsMobile,
    LinksMobile,  } from "./NavBarStyle";
const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <List>
                    <Elements>
                        <Links href="#home">Home</Links>
                    </Elements>
                    <Elements>
                        <Links href="#sobre">Sobre</Links>
                    </Elements>
                    <Elements>
                        <Links href="#api">Api's</Links>
                    </Elements>
                </List>
            </Container>
            <ContainerMobile>
                
                <ListMobile>
                    <ElementsMobile>
                        <LinksMobile href="#home">Home</LinksMobile>
                    </ElementsMobile>
                    <ElementsMobile>
                        <LinksMobile href="#sobre">Sobre</LinksMobile>
                    </ElementsMobile>
                    <ElementsMobile>
                        <LinksMobile href="#api">Api's</LinksMobile>
                    </ElementsMobile>
                </ListMobile>
            </ContainerMobile>
        </>
    );
};

export default NavBar;
